Package: parsr
Type: Package
Title: Parse Arguments in R Functions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Daniel", "Morillo", email = "danivmorillo@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/CCOMS-UAM/parsr
Maintainer: Daniel Morillo <danivmorillo@gmail.com>
Description: This package is intended to help following the "fail fast"
    principle when developing R software.
    It also intends to allow enough flexibility to embrace the principle of
    "being lax in your input".
Depends:
    R               (>= 4.0.5),
